text: Kaadu moominiinik namma butta toome tet tekkekii, ken nammayih fan bicisa, kaadu ken naqmmayak tiyák teyna, akittot taturtekii, taturte tiyâ lih oomiya, Yallih amrih gacca ittam fanah. Kaadu is tuduure tet tekkekii, ken nammayih fan qadlil bicisa kaadu abinnaanih cokmi qadlil aba, diggah Yalli qadli-abá kicna
